com.jlefebure.spring.boot.minio

类 MinioService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jlefebure.spring.boot.minio.MinioService

  • @Service
public class MinioService
extends Object
    Service class to interact with Minio bucket. This class is register as a bean and use the properties defined in MinioConfigurationProperties. All methods return an MinioException which wrap the Minio SDK exception. The bucket name is provided with the one defined in the configuration properties.
    作者:
    Jordan LEFEBURE This service adapetd with minio sdk 7.0.x, Mostafa Jalambadani
